{"id": "art-114", "label": "Art. 114", "title": "Art. 114", "slug": "art-114", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 114 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_140169667\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2333\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_140169667\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Exerci&#355;iul</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>atribu&#355;iilor</span> prev&#259;zute la </span><s><span\nstyle='color:#E51C23'>art. 113</span></s><u><span style='color:#569748'>art.\n113</span></u><span style='color:black'> lit. b), c)</span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>, d)</span></u><span style='color:black'> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> f) va putea fi delegat consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv directoratului, prin actul\nconstitutiv sau prin hot&#259;râre a adun&#259;rii generale extraordinare a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>. Delegarea <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la </span><s><span style='color:#E51C23'>art. 113</span></s><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>art. 113</span></u><span style='color:black'> lit. c) nu\npoate privi domeniul <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> activitatea\nprincipal&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1023844225\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2332\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1023844225\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul în care consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul, este mandatat s&#259; îndeplineasc&#259; m&#259;sura\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>113 lit. f)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. 220<sup>1</sup>\nse aplic&#259; deciziilor consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv celor ale directoratului, în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1117396474\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2331\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1117396474\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cazul în care\nconsiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv\ndirectoratul este mandatat s&#259; îndeplineasc&#259; m&#259;surile\nprev&#259;zute de art. </b></span><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>113 lit. b) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> c)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>131 alin. (4) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (5)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, ale art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>132</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> alin. (6) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (7), precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nprevederile art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>133</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> se aplic&#259; deciziilor consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv celor ale directoratului, în\nmod corespunz&#259;tor. Societatea va fi reprezentat&#259; în <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;&#259;</span> de c&#259;tre persoana desemnat&#259; de\n<span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span> <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span>\ndintre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> ei, care va îndeplini mandatul\ncu care a fost îns&#259;rcinat&#259;, pân&#259; ce adunarea general&#259;,\nconvocat&#259; în acest scop, va alege o alt&#259; persoan&#259;.</span></b><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_798650466\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2330\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_798650466\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>*) Curtea <span class=SpellE>Constitu&#355;ional&#259;</span>\nadmite <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> de <span class=SpellE>neconstitu&#355;ionalitate</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> constat&#259; c&#259; <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;ia</span>\nlegislativ&#259; cuprins&#259; în art. 114 alin. (3) din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>31/1990</span><span style='color:black'>, care nu permite\ncontestarea în <span class=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span>, pe calea <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunii</span> în anulare prev&#259;zute de art. 132 din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, a deciziilor consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv directoratului luate în\nexercitarea <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iei</span> delegate de majorare a\ncapitalului social, este <span class=SpellE>neconstitu&#355;ional&#259;</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}